import { Button } from "@material-ui/core";
import React, { useContext } from "react";
import "./dashbord.css";
import Grid from "@material-ui/core/Grid";
import NewContext from "./newContex";
import { PropTypes } from "prop-types";

const NewButtons = (itemValue, handelClick) => {
  return (
    <Grid
      item
      xs={12}
      className="literals"
      container
      direction="row"
      justify="flex-start"
      alignItems="flex-start"
    >
      <Grid item xs={2} className="part1">
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          +
        </Button>
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          -
        </Button>
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          *
        </Button>
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          =
        </Button>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={2} className="part1">
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          /
        </Button>
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          %
        </Button>
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          x²
        </Button>
        <Button value={itemValue} onClick={handelClick}>
          √
        </Button>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={8} className="part2">
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          1
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          2
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          3
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          4
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          5
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          6
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          7
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          8
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          9
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          0
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          .
        </Button>
        <Button name="" onClick={handelClick}>
          C
        </Button>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
};
NewButtons.propTypes = {
  numberValue: PropTypes.string,
  handelClick: PropTypes.func,
};
export default NewButtons;
